you know what I mean?

443
00:21:08.884 --> 00:21:09.950
No.

444
00:21:11.937 --> 00:21:13.454
Sometimes you judge people...

445
00:21:14.273 --> 00:21:16.056
I mean. we all do.

446
00:21:16.125 --> 00:21:17.625
Sometimes you just...

447
00:21:18.394 --> 00:21:19.460
