465
00:22:33.202 --> 00:22:34.202
No.

466
00:22:35.104 --> 00:22:36.403
Clay. you don't understand.

467
00:22:36.472 --> 00:22:37.905
I do understand.

468
00:22:37.974 --> 00:22:40.001
Every drama has
to be your drama.
or it doesn't count.

469
00:22:40.025 --> 00:22:42.192
Somehow this is all about you.
