482
00:23:14.910 --> 00:23:16.860
Hannah...
Sheri. Jeff is...

483
00:23:19.849 --> 00:23:20.864
You two okay?

484
00:23:21.867 --> 00:23:23.600
Yeah. we're okay. Mr. Porter.

485
00:23:23.669 --> 00:23:26.437
